item.title: LIVE @ Aftermath 1994 - DJ Cykophuk
item.description: This is my "Back in the Day". Aftermath was a 600 capacity club in Chicago with 3 levels, an active dungeon, a biker poolhall and the very finest of crowds. I miss the hell outta that place. We recorded an entire Saturday Night with a VHS deck and years later, I had it mastered, for old times sake. This is disc 2 of 5. At this point of the night, I'm warmed up and not yet fucked up...so not bad. Enjoy some old ass Industrial & Goth mixin'.
